    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自特朗普赢得以来，美国的10年收益率首次下降到4％以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自10月以来，基准国债的收益率首次下降到4％以下，因为华尔街对美国经济将从唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战中最终更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街在贸易冲击上遍布资产：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的影响周四遍布全球市场，击落股票并促进了进入固定收益避风港的飞行。美国股票和美元对猜测总统的贸易攻势的一些最糟糕的销售将阻碍美国经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税使喂养处于艰难的位置，提高增长和价格担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/tariffs-put-fed-in-tough-spot-raise-growth-and-price-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）周三宣布的一系列积极的关税将使美联储（Federal Reserve）的工作显着复杂化，因为它努力消除通货膨胀并避免经济下滑，可能使官员处于待观察模式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/tariffs-put-fed-in-tough-spot-raise-growth-and-price-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汽车制造商闲置植物，随着特朗普的关税打击而重新考虑价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[生效仅几个小时后，唐纳德·特朗普总统对进口汽车的25％关税已经在全球回荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/trump-spares-automakers-from-more-pain-in-reciprocal-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 22:09:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普启动关税时，比特币屈服于资产低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bitcoin-settles-in-narrow-range-after-trump-sets-trade-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统对全球贸易伙伴征收关税之后，比特币和其他重大加密货币下跌，引发了风险资产的低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/bitcoin-settles-in-narrow-range-after-trump-sets-trade-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:20:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
